      "entity_id": null,
      "paper_id": "paper_1",
      "text_span_id": "results_1",
      "text": "AURKA level was significantly increased in both test groups (p < 0.001). At the protein level, AURKA was significantly higher in both cancer groups compared to the control group (p < 0.001).",
